convert subsystems to the system type T function make_systems_with_type!(systems::Vector, rs::ReactionSystem, include_zero_odes=true) where  resize!(systems, length(get_systems(rs))) for (i,sys) in enumerate(get_systems(rs)) if sys isa ReactionSystem systems[i] = convert(T, sys, include_zero_odes=include_zero_odes) elseif sys isa T systems[i] = sys else try if (T <: MT.AbstractTimeDependentSystem) && (sys isa MT.AbstractTimeIndependentSystem) systems[i] = MT.convert_system(T, sys, get_iv(rs)) else systems[i] = MT.convert_system(T, sys) end catch e error("ModelingToolkit does not currently support convert_system(
(typeof(sys)))") end end end systems end merge constraint components with the ReactionSystem components also handles removing BC and constant species
